Class# IODispatchQueue

macOS 10.15+

```
class IODispatchQueue : OSObject, IODispatchQueueInterface
```

## [Topics](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue#topics)

### [Instance Methods](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue#3223545)

[`- Cancel`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3438188-cancel)Stops the queue from dequeueing any further tasks, and notifies the specified handler when all in-flight tasks finish.[`- Dispatch`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3223267-dispatch)[`- DispatchAsync`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3438190-dispatchasync)Schedule a block for asynchronous execution on the current queue.[`- DispatchAsync_f`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3438191-dispatchasync_f)Schedule a C-style function for asynchrous execution on the current queue.[`- DispatchConcurrent`](/documentation/driverkit/iodispatchqueue/dispatchconcurrent)[`- DispatchConcurrent_f`](/documentation/driverkit/iodispatchqueue/dispatchconcurrent_f)[`- DispatchSync`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3438192-dispatchsync)Schedule a block for synchronous execution on the current queue.[`- DispatchSync_f`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3438193-dispatchsync_f)Schedule a C-style function for synchronous execution on the current queue.[`- GetName`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3438194-getname)Returns the name of the queue as a C string.[`- OnQueue`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3438196-onqueue)Returns a Boolean value that indicates whether the current thread matches the dispatch queue's thread. [`- RunAction`](/documentation/driverkit/iodispatchqueue/runaction)[`- SetPort`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3223275-setport)[`- SetPort_Impl`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3223276-setport_impl)[`- Sleep`](/documentation/driverkit/iodispatchqueue/sleep)[`- SleepWithDeadline`](/documentation/driverkit/iodispatchqueue/sleepwithdeadline)[`- SleepWithTimeout`](/documentation/driverkit/iodispatchqueue/sleepwithtimeout)[`- Wakeup`](/documentation/driverkit/iodispatchqueue/wakeup)[`- WakeupWithOptions`](/documentation/driverkit/iodispatchqueue/wakeupwithoptions)[`- free`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3438197-free)Performs any final cleanup for the dispatch queue object.[`- getMetaClass`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3223279-getmetaclass)[`- init`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3438198-init)Initializes the dispatch queue object.### [Type Methods](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue#3223546)

[`+ Create`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3438189-create)Creates a new dispatch queue object.[`+ Create_Call`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3223264-create_call)[`+ Create_Impl`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3223265-create_impl)[`+ Create_Invoke`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3223266-create_invoke)[`+ Log`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3438195-log)Log the current execution context with respect to any queues the current thread holds.[`+ SetPort_Invoke`](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue/3223277-setport_invoke)## [Relationships](/documentation/kernel/iodispatchqueue#relationships)
